June 14, 2017 / Susan, Colin and Rabia examine and analyze last week's oral arguments before the Maryland Court of Special Appeals by state and defense attorneys in Adnan Syed's ongoing case.

Episode scoring music by AnimalWeapon, Blue Dot Sessions, Chris Zabriskie, Fleslit, H-LR, Jahzzar, Remain, Uncanny Valleys, VYVCH, and Sym5.
